    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A specialized version of Mizudama no Jutsu, this technique has you produce large amounts of saliva, which is spit out and hardened. Make a ranged attack roll, which deals damage on hit based on your size category: Large (2d4 water damage), Huge (2d8 water damage), Gargantuan (4d6 water damage) or Colossal (4d8 water damage).<br><br>You may fire additional bullets (up to 1 bullet per 4 levels total). Each bullet requires an attack roll, can target any creature within range (even creatures already targeted by other teppoudama), and increases the Cost by 2 Chakra.</p>\n\n\n\n",
